OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,FThe UK Government has issued a call
OL,8,Ffor information as it "moves closer"
OL,9,Fto a deal with the EU aimed at
OL,10,Fsmoothing post-Brexit friction in
OL,11,Fagrifood trade.
OL,13,FOfficials are negotiating a deal to
OL,14,Fmake agrifood trade with the EU
OL,15,Feasier, cheaper and quicker for
OL,16,FBritish businesses to export and
OL,17,Fimport.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
