OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773027580
OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,FIt is aiming to cut red tape, increase
OL,8,Fchoice for consumers and put downward
OL,9,Fpressure on food price inflation with
OL,10,Fa proposed start date in mid-2027.
OL,12,FExports of food and agricultural
OL,13,Fproducts to the EU since 2018 have
OL,14,Ffallen by 22% ` almost #4 billion in
OL,15,Freal terms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
