OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,FThe Sanitary and Phytosanitary (SPS)
OL,8,Fagreement aims to facilitate the
OL,9,Fsmooth flow of agrifood goods,
OL,10,Fincluding plants, from Great Britain
OL,11,Fto Northern Ireland, protecting the UK
OL,12,Finternal market while maintaining
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland's unique access to
OL,14,Fthe EU single market.
OL,16,FTraders would no longer need
OL,17,Fregulatory certificates, checks or
OL,18,Fpaperwork for most agrifood goods
OL,19,Fmoving from Great Britain to Northern
OL,20,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773027580
OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,FThe UK Government has launched a six-
OL,8,Fweek call for information to
OL,9,Funderstand how it can support
OL,10,Fbusinesses to make the most of this
OL,11,Fopportunity.
OL,13,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,14,Fsaid that ensuring Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fbenefits from the agreement has been a
OL,16,F"guiding principle of our
OL,17,Fnegotiations".
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773027580
OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,F"This deal will make it easier for
OL,8,Fbusinesses to move agrifood goods from
OL,9,FGreat Britain to Northern Ireland,
OL,10,Fcutting unnecessary paperwork and
OL,11,Fslashing costs," she said.
OL,13,F"At the same time, Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fwill retain its unique dual market ` a
OL,15,Fposition unmatched elsewhere in
OL,16,FEurope."
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,19,Fdescribed a "significant milestone for
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland" as the UK moves
OL,21,Ftowards an agreement with the EU.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@PO]uD@AOUxD@HO]{D@MOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773027580
OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,F"This will make it easier, cheaper and
OL,8,Fquicker for British businesses to
OL,9,Fexport and import food, animals and
OL,10,Fplants," he said.
OL,12,F"By removing complex checks and
OL,13,Fpaperwork for the vast majority of
OL,14,Fthis trade, an agreement will reduce
OL,15,Fcosts and red tape for local
OL,16,Fbusinesses while fully protecting the
OL,17,Fintegrity of the UK internal market.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@HO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773027580
OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,F"This agreement will not only
OL,8,Freinforce Northern Ireland's unique
OL,9,Fdual market access, but also ensure
OL,10,Fthat we continue to uphold our
OL,11,Fcommitments under the Good Friday
OL,12,FAgreement while securing a better
OL,13,Feconomic future."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
