PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773027580
OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,FUlster Farmers' Union president
OL,8,FWilliam Irvine said: "The UFU welcomes
OL,9,Fprogress on the UK-EU SPS agreement
OL,10,Fnegotiations and the opportunities it
OL,11,Fpresents for the agrifood sector. A
OL,12,Fhuge amount of work has gone in at UFU
OL,13,Flevel over many years to get to this
OL,14,Fpoint.
OL,16,F"Many Windsor Framework issues we have
OL,17,Fbeen lobbying on can be addressed
OL,18,Funder a closer UK-EU relationship and
OL,19,Fit is our hope and desire that this is
OL,20,Freflected in any future agreement.
OL,26,@pD@VOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773027580
OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,F"An agreement on SPS matters between
OL,8,Fthe UK and EU can bring real long-term
OL,9,Fcertainty for our members and the
OL,10,Fwider agrifood industry. If a
OL,11,Fcomprehensive agreement is achieved,
OL,12,Fit will go a long way in freeing up
OL,13,Fthe movement of agrifood goods from GB
OL,14,Fto NI and ensuring farmers across the
OL,15,FUK are on a level playing field.
OL,17,F"However, it is essential that any
OL,18,Ffuture agreement is implemented as
OL,19,Fquickly as possible so that Northern
OL,20,FIreland farmers and food businesses
OL,21,Fcan begin to see the benefits."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
