CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773027580
OL,3,CCall for information as UK 'moves
OL,4,Ccloser' to agreement with EU on
OL,5,Cagrifood trade
OL,7,FBusinesses in Northern Ireland have
OL,8,Fbeen asked to engage with their trade
OL,9,Fbody or industry association and their
OL,10,Fsupply chain to understand changes
OL,11,Fthat may apply to them, as well as
OL,12,Fsigning up for Defra alerts.
OL,14,FThey are also asked to respond to the
OL,15,Fcall for information and share views
OL,16,Fon what support their business needs
OL,17,Fto prepare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
